data.title: Just Java Cafe! Wow what Tragic Memories i have of this place. The Brothers.
data.text:
Over the Years I have been a Disc Jockey all over the place! 
From Imperial Beach, To Crescent City, and all the way to Mexicali, Down to Punto Colonet, Mexico, And even at the Just Java Cafe from the very Beginning. The Just Java cafe has changed ownership a few times and it is a very nice Quaint Banquet hall and reception Hall. I have done Quinceneras, Weddings and even sound for a Born again Christian revival, healing cult type of Show... All in All the Just Java Cafe has seen it all too...
